HEADWORD: Self-knowing
<hw>Self`-know"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Knowing one's self, or one's own character, powers, and
limitations.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Knowing of itself, without help from
another.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Self-knowledge</ent>⟦br⟧
